text
@/*
   FvwmButtons v2.0.41-plural-Z-alpha, copyright 1996, Jarl Totland

 * This module, and the entire GoodStuff program, and the concept for
 * interfacing this module to the Window Manager, are all original work
 * by Robert Nation
